#: /16x9/Custom_1107_DialogConfirmFactoryReset.xml
msgctxt "#31467"
msgid "Welcome to Madnox! For the best experience, we recommend applying the default settings. This will configure all visual options and features. Would you like to apply the Madnox recommended settings now?"
msgstr "Madnox tizimiga xush kelibsiz! Eng yaxshi foydalanish tajribasi uchun standart sozlamalarni qo'llashni tavsiya etamiz. Bu barcha vizual parametrlar va funksiyalarni sozlaydi. Madnox tavsiya etgan sozlamalarni hozir qo'llamoqchimisiz?"

#: /16x9/Custom_1107_DialogConfirmFactoryReset.xml
msgctxt "#31468"
msgid "This will restore all skin settings to their original defaults.[CR][CR]Your current customizations will be lost.[CR]Are you sure you want to continue?"
msgstr "Bu barcha interfeys sozlamalarini dastlabki holatiga qaytaradi.[CR][CR]Hozirgi moslashtirishlaringiz yo'qoladi.[CR]Davom etishni tasdiqlaysizmi?"

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31470"
msgid "Restore Madnox skin settings to day 1 out of the box startup values. Only affects skin settings, does not alter or change anything else like scripts or plugins."
msgstr "Madnox interfeys sozlamalarini dastlabki o'rnatilgan holatiga qaytarish. Bu faqat interfeys sozlamalariga ta'sir qiladi, skript yoki plaginlar kabi boshqa narsalarni o'zgartirmaydi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31471"
msgid "Allows customization of default media flags without requiring outside hacks to the skin. This allows you to custom select which video container icons will be displayed for WebDL, 1080p, 720p etc. This can be reset at any time."
msgstr "Tizimga tashqi o'zgartirishlar kiritmasdan standart media bayroqchalarini moslashtirish imkonini beradi. Bu sizga WebDL, 1080p, 720p va hokazolar uchun qaysi video konteyner piktogrammalari ko'rsatilishini tanlash imkonini beradi. Buni istalgan vaqtda qayta tiklash mumkin."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31472"
msgid "Enables setting of the color of \"In-Progress\" bar feature."
msgstr "\"Jarayonda\" paneli funksiyasining rangini sozlashni yoqadi."

