#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31506"
msgid "Current built-in revision level of the default Madnox values to reset / initialize the skin."
msgstr "Interfeysni qayta tiklash / faollashtirish uchun standart Madnox qiymatlarining joriy o'rnatilgan versiyasi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31507"
msgid "Select if an intro video will play when Kodi is first started. None: No video, Built-In: Kodi's release level intro video, Custom: Pick video of your choice to display."
msgstr "Kodi birinchi marta ishga tushganda kirish videosi ijro etilishini tanlang. Yo'q: video ijro etilmaydi, Standart: Kodining standart kirish videosi, Maxsus: Ko'rsatish uchun o'zingiz xohlagan videoni tanlang."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31508"
msgid "This setting forces the media flag to resolution flag as 4K or 2160p providing user icon control without skin modifcations."
msgstr "Ushbu sozlama interfeysni o'zgartirmasdan foydalanuvchiga piksel o'lchami bayrog'ini 4K yoki 2160p deb belgilash imkonini beradi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31509"
msgid "Change the stars color displayed in the video info line. Click to cycle through fixed colors or select a custom color."
msgstr "Video ma'lumotlari satrida ko'rsatiladigan yulduzchalar rangini o'zgartiring. Ruxsat etilgan ranglar bo'ylab o'tish uchun bosing yoki maxsus rangni tanlang."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31510"
msgid "Allows star ratings style to use a custom color when it is set to \"Custom\"."
msgstr "Yulduzchalar reytingi uslubi \"Maxsus\" deb o'rnatilganda undan foydalanish imkonini beradi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31511"
msgid "Dedicated addon for Madnox required for Piers+. Moves all free running scripts to a dedicated addon for security purposes."
msgstr "Piers+ uchun zarur bo'lgan Madnox maxsus plagini. Xavfsizlik maqsadida barcha ishlaydigan mustaqil skriptlarni maxsus plaginga o'tkazadi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31512"
msgid "TMDbHelper provides several tools to assist skinners with retrieving information from TMDb, OMDb and Trakt APIs."
msgstr "TMDbHelper interfeys yaratuvchilariga TMDb, OMDb va Trakt APIlaridan ma'lumot olishda yordam beradigan bir nechta vositalarni taqdim etadi."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31513"
msgid "Wikipedia addon for Kodi."
msgstr "Kodi uchun Wikipedia plagini."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
msgctxt "#31514"
msgid "Advanced CinemaVision replacement that can be enabled to replace Madnox's built in simpler CinemaMode. Allows the ultimate CinemaMode experience and customisation."
msgstr "Madnox-ning o'rnatilgan oddiy CinemaMode rejimi o'rniga faollashtirilishi mumkin bo'lgan kengaytirilgan CinemaVision muqobili. Maksimal darajada CinemaMode rejimi va moslashtirish imkonini beradi."

#: /16x9/Includes_CustomSelect.xml
msgctxt "#31515"
msgid "Blur with color"
msgstr "Rang bilan xiralashtirish"

