msgctxt "#31524"
msgid "Allows changes to the ratings to convert between floating numbers or as a percentage. Affects TMDb & IMDb, all others remain as their default display."
msgstr "Reytinglarni o'nlik sonlar yoki foizlar ko'rinishiga o'zgartirish imkonini beradi. TMDb va IMDb-ga ta'sir qiladi, boshqalari standart holatda qoladi."

