msgstr "Bu interfeys tezkor tugmalarining .properties faylini joriy 3 modulli plagin tuzilishiga qayta yozadi. Faqat fon tasvirlarida muammolar bo'lsa yoki pleylistlar ishlamayotgan bo'lsa ishlating."

#: /16x9/SkinSettings.xml
msgctxt "#31527"
msgid "This will reactivate the addons installer. Only run if addons were not installed when skin was first installed."
msgstr "Bu plaginlarni o'rnatuvchini qayta faollashtiradi. Faqat interfeys birinchi marta o'rnatilganda plaginlar o'rnatilmagan bo'lsa ishlating."

#: /16x9/Includes_Settings.xml
